sourcesContent: import React, { Component } from 'react'; export function Atds({title,body,img,firstIconTitle,firstIconBody,secondIconTitle,secondIconBody,numbers}) { return ( <> ADS title {title} ADS body {body} ADS img first icon img {firstIconTitle} first icon title {firstIconBody} second icon img {secondIconTitle} second icon title {secondIconBody} {numbers.map((e,index)=>{return <> num title {index +1} {e.title} num value {index +1} {e.number} num title {index +1} {e.title} num value {index +1} {e.number} })} ); } export default Atds
